**Build forward, never backward.** Migrate data and delete old code — no backwards-compat shims, aliases, or translation layers. In a single-owner codebase, change the code and update all call sites.

**No fallback code paths** or "just in case" error recovery unless explicitly asked for. Fail visibly — don't swallow errors or silently degrade. When resilience matters the human will say so; when unsure, stop and ask.
